  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Pet Care & Transport Driver",
  "description": "<h3>About the Role</h3><p>We are looking for an animal-loving, responsible, and physically fit Pet Transport Driver to join a dedicated pet care team. This role focuses on the safe pickup and drop-off of pets, mainly dogs and occasionally cats. When not on transport duties, you will assist with daily pet care operations.</p><p>This position is well suited for someone who genuinely enjoys working with animals, especially dogs, and is comfortable in a hands-on environment.</p><h3>Key Responsibilities</h3><ul><li><p>Safely transport pets between homes, boarding facilities, vets, groomers, and other locations</p></li><li><p>Confidently handle dogs of all sizes, including large and strong breeds</p></li><li><p>Assist with daily pet care tasks such as walking, feeding, cleaning, and basic grooming support</p></li><li><p>Maintain cleanliness, hygiene, and safety of the vehicle at all times</p></li><li><p>Communicate professionally and warmly with pet owners and team members</p></li></ul><h3>Requirements</h3><ul><li><p>Based in Singapore with a valid Class 3 driving licence and a clean driving record</p></li><li><p>Comfortable handling large, active dogs</p></li><li><p>Physically fit and able to manage pets safely and confidently</p></li><li><p>Genuine love for animals; owning a pet is an advantage</p></li><li><p>Prior experience in pet care, pet transport, dog walking, or animal shelters is an advantage</p></li><li><p>Reliable, responsible, and punctual</p></li></ul><h3>Working Arrangement</h3><ul><li><p>Three weekdays and one weekend day per week</p></li><li><p>Immediate start preferred</p></li></ul><h3>Salary and Benefits</h3><ul><li><p>Supportive and animal-focused work environment</p></li><li><p>Hands-on experience working with pets on a daily basis</p></li></ul>",
